qa.question: James writes a 3-page letter to 2 different friends twice a week.  How many pages does he write a year?

result.english_raw: James writes 3 pages to 2 different friends twice a week, which is 24 pages a month and 288 pages a year.

he.raw: בשנה, ג'יימס כותב שלושים עמודים מכתבים - שש מכתבים בכל שבוע.
he.cot: A: James writes a 3-page letter to two different friends twice a week. He writes 3x2x52 = 312 pages in a year. The answer is 312.

ja.raw: James will write 624 pages of letters in a year. He will write two 3-page letters to two different friends twice a week, which adds up to 24 pages a week, or 1248 pages a year.

es.raw: James escribe 6 páginas por semana, lo que equivale a 312 páginas al año.
